    <topic>
        <title>Introduction</title>
        <text>&lt;span  rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;In this lesson, you will learn two (2) ways of serving the food to the guest: Leaving the food on the table and setting the table for the guest.&lt;/span&gt;</text>
