    <topic>
        <title>Serving the Food Order</title>
        <text>&lt;span  rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;There are two (2) types of serving the food order to the guest: leaving the tray on the table and setting the table for the guest.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;br  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;strong  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;1. Leaving the tray on the table&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span  rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;span  rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;This is where you will just leave the tray on the table. This is a common option by the guests who do not want to be disturbed and want to spend the time alone as quickly as possible.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;br  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;strong  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;2. Setting the food on the table&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span  rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;span  rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 19.578125px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 50px;&quot;&gt;This is where you get the food from the tray and set it up on the table.&lt;/span&gt;</text>
